snippet.title: The Disturbing Disappearance of Amber Tuccaro
snippet.description:
I’m not saying Pat Carson or any of the other names he goes under is responsible for any thing at all, just reporting on what others have said and blogged. Sources linked below:


Amber Tuccaro vanished in Alberta, Canada, after getting a ride with a stranger on her way into Edmonton. A call she made while in his car was recorded, and she knew something was horribly wrong, and she sounded terrified. What happened to Amber Tuccaro has never been discovered, and remains an unsolved mystery.
